74
00:07:43,498 --> 00:07:47,061
So then what is the essential quality or principle behind a

75
00:07:47,101 --> 00:07:47,721
visual novel?

76
00:07:56,970 --> 00:07:59,993
Watch on screen, the essential quality of a visual novel.

77
00:08:00,013 --> 00:08:06,198
